---
// About section component with profile information
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2 class="about-title">Nicola Beirer</h2>
        <p class="about-lead">
          Software Engineer who likes to build things.
        </p>
        <p class="about-description">
          This blog is where I share my projects and what I've learned along the way. You'll also find other random posts.
        </p>
        <div class="about-interests">
          <h3>Main areas of interest:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Piloting</li>
            <li>Traveling</li>
            <li>Exercising</li>
            <li>Building things for others</li>
            <li>Learning things!</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="about-personal">
          When I'm not coding, you can find me doing jiu-jitsu, muay thai, cycling, playing sports, flying planes or reading!
        </p>
        
